data.description: Cute Ranch that has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. One full bath is in the master bedroom. Almost on an acre (.89). Great views from the front and the back yard. Country setting. Close to the freeway. Quick access to Springfield. Columbus and London aren't far either. Updates include water softener and more.
